nodes.text: The Tarabba sector was a sector in the Outer Rim Territories, and contained the Utapau system, whose primary world was the sinkhole planet of Utapau. The capital of the Tarabba sector was Tarabba Prime. The sector was located between the Tantra and Quence sectors.

The Utapau system was taken by the Confederacy of Independent Systems during the Clone Wars, and was freed by Obi-Wan Kenobi in time for the newly-established Galactic Empire to assume control of the sector.
